name: Birth Year Block - Year of the Dragon
description:
A handmade, hardwood keepsake block celebrating baby's year of birth. Based on the chinese zodiac, each year is named after an animal with traits said to belong to those born in that year. 

For 2012, Year of the Dragon:

You are...
...intelligent...
..energetic..
..imaginative...
..ambitious..

See if your baby grows into a little person with the characteristics listed on the block.

This listing is for one block. Available in colors pink, blue or mint green. 

Solid wood block, 2 1/2" cube

Handmade in my home studio in California.
Copyrighted design.

options.name: Available in pink, blue or green

name: Birth Year Box - Year of the Dragon
description:
A wooden, keepsake box for all of those special people born in the Year of the Dragon.

A special place to keep all of your treasures and special things that make you unique. Inside of box has a glassine envelope with the characteristics of the Dragon. Great for gifting!

Hinged Box size: 5 1/2 " wide by 4 1/2" long by 1 1/2" deep

Colors available: bright green, turquoise, raspberry, tangerine and pastel pink, pastel blue and mint green. 

Handmade in my home studio in California. 
Copyrighted design.

name: Heart Good Egg
description:
A solid, wood heart egg! A special egg for someone who's been a "Good Egg" in your life. 

The heart egg is the perfect way to say "I Love You,"
"Happy Anniversary" or even "Will you marry me?"

Available in pink, turquoise, or green.

Egg size is 2 1/2 " H x 1 3/4" diam.

Gift packaging available. 

Handprinted and handpainted in my home studio in California. 

Original design, copyrighted 2011
